Package: rollr2
Title: Roll Tabletop RPG Dice from Notation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Felix", "Mil", , "felix.mil@esqlabs.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Parses and rolls tabletop RPG dice notation such as "2d20+2",
    reporting individual die results, totals, and the outcome distribution
    across repeated rolls.
